node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nice Kicks on July 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'pjtucker #latepost Ok so Michelle is our assistant trainer and she stepped up to do her first game as head trainer the other night.. Our trainer loves Jordan 1s and wears them EVERY GAME! She loves em too but has never had a pair.. So y'all know had to get her right for her first game soi surprised her #shealmostmademecry #shesthebest #fearthedeer #family #wearyakicks'.

Photo shared by Nice Kicks on July 18, 2021 tagging @bucks, and @giannis_an34. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and text that says 'EX NICE Nice Kicks @nicekicks The @Bucks are 3-0 since Giannis wore black Air Force 1s to Game 3'.

node.text: Giannis been in a different mode since bringing out the black AF1s 🥷😤
